@page "/"

<PageTitle>Home</PageTitle>

<h1>Welcome to MSFD Blazor API Demo</h1>

<div class="alert alert-info">
    <h4>Project Overview</h4>
    <p>This is a Blazor WebAssembly application created for the Microsoft Full-Stack Integration course, showcasing modern web development techniques and API integration.</p>

</div>

<h3>What is this project?</h3>
<p>
    The <strong>MSFD Blazor API Demo</strong> is an educational project built with:
</p>
<ul>
    <li><strong>Frontend:</strong> Blazor WebAssembly for interactive single-page application experience</li>
    <li><strong>API Integration:</strong> Demonstrates consuming external APIs (GitHub API)</li>
    <li><strong>Markdown Rendering:</strong> Dynamic content rendering using Markdig</li>
</ul>

<h3>Key Features</h3>
<ul>
    <li>GitHub API integration for fetching user profile and repository data</li>
    <li>Dynamic markdown to HTML conversion</li>
    <li>Responsive design with Bootstrap styling</li>
    <li>Cross-origin request handling (CORS)</li>
    <li>Real-time hot reload during development</li>
</ul>

